name: Madame President (Anime Golden boy) NSFW / SFW
description:
Hello :3

Today I present you Madame President, who is managed Japanese IT company where the protagonist of the anime "Golden Boy" Kintaro got a job (for a short time :3).

NSFW / SFW model

LoRA was trained on Animefull-pruned.cpkt due to best compitability with all anime checkpoint models.

9th epoch of 10, 4260 steps (2130 with batch size 2).

0.8 - 1 strength of Lora is the best radius. I prefer 0.9.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Main tokens:

MadamePresident, mature female, milf, blonde hair, long hair, wavy hair, lipstick, makeup, earring, red nails, nail polish

For her office lady outfit:

black pantyhose, black pencil skirt, highheels, skirt suit, blue jacket;

(blue blouse or blue skirt also good prompts).

For her red dress / bodysuit outfit:

center opening, red dress, covered nipples, helterneck, highheels;

(Red bodysuit and latex also work).

Optional: Sunglasses.

If you don't need red clothes put them to negative prompt.

Also LoRA was trained with some arts including nsfw poses.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, lollypop and animesharp.

use extention "dddetailer" (very useful extension for faces. You forget about face inpainting with it).

·         use SD Upscale script in img2img (For me 1.25-1.5x with AnimeSharp, UltraSharp or fatal anime is good on 0.2-0.3 denoising strengh);

·         Use inpaint and sketch for other details;

·         Use Photoshop.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!

Other works.
